{
  "stem": "10353.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Hungarian plainclothes detectives.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They processed me at the police station in Budapest after they interrogated me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some very physical interrogation, beating up and so on and so on, and--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They tried-- they didn't tell me what it is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although I knew-- I had a proclivity of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what's happening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] They asked-- there were anti-Jewish laws at that time that, you know, you could not have any physical, intimate connection with non-Jews, which was also under heavy, heavy prison threats.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they tried to tell me that they know that I had some intimate connection with non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- but they-- they tried to divert me from what it is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they finally said, what did I-- what kind of documents did I-- I mean, I didn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I-- I was innocent in the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wasn't involved in that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They finally brought in the gendarmes, you know, the ones with the feathers-- feather hats.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they [? chained ?] me, shackled me, and they took me down to the train station.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were traveling all day, until we came-- until about 11:00 in the night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the train stopped, and we got off the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very, very dark, and in the distance, I saw a building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took me into that building, and it was about 11:00, 11:30 at night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there the interrogations started all over again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The gendarmes were standing by either side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was an interrogator, a civilian man who was talking very crudely, and yelling and shouting, and slapping me from time to time that I'm not telling the truth.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
